    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel like \"moving on\". it feels like i'm just... haunting my own life. like i'm stuck in this body that doesn't belong to me anymore, just going through the motions while the real me is long gone. it's exhausting. honestly, it feels more like a burden than a life at this point.",
